                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When offered a gift worth at least 50 gp, the k'nonna must attempt a <span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"will\" data-pf2-label=\"Gilded Fascination DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"20\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Will</span> saving throw; if the gift is worth at least 100 gp, the DC is instead <span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"will\" data-pf2-label=\"Gilded Fascination (Higher) DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"25\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Will</span>.</p>\n<p>If they fail the save, the k'nonna accepts the gift, becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Fascinated]{Fascinated} until the end of their next turn, and cannot attack while fascinated. On a critical failure, the fascination lasts for 1 minute.</p>\n<p>Offering a gift is an Interact action, and offering multiple gifts in the same round has no additional effect.</p>"
